95
00:06:55,015 --> 00:06:57,975
<i>Danger showed up
a couple of years back.</i>

96
00:06:59,295 --> 00:07:03,615
<i>He'd come visiting L.A. with Ervel,
his mama's new boyfriend.</i>

97
00:07:04,215 --> 00:07:08,855
